## How to Use This Index

This index provides **one-line summaries** of each cross-cutting concern. When implementing features:

1. Agents automatically detect relevant concerns based on keywords
2. Full concern documentation is loaded on-demand
3. You can explicitly tag features with concerns during `/spec`

**Token Cost:** ~500 tokens (always loaded)
**Full Docs:** ~1000 tokens each (loaded when needed)

