## Loading Triggers

Agents automatically load full concern docs when they detect:

| Concern | Keywords | Feature Tags |
|---------|----------|--------------|
| **Authentication** | login, signup, token, session, oauth | auth, authentication |
| **Authorization** | permission, role, access, policy, rbac, abac | authz, authorization, permissions |
| **Multi-Tenancy** | tenant, organization, workspace, isolation | multi-tenant, tenancy |
| **Caching** | cache, redis, memcached, performance | caching, performance |
| **Logging** | log, audit, tracking, monitoring | logging, observability |
| **Database** | table, column, migration, schema | database, data-model |
| **APIs** | endpoint, route, controller, api | api, integration |

